name: caprylanilide

Therefore, the addition of the alkyl chain could contribute to a decrease of 35°C. Combining these adjustments, the overall prediction is as follows:

  Amide group: +80°C
  Aliphatic chain (7 methylene groups x -5°C each): -35°C
